  <summary date="2021-06-30T15:06:29Z" status="Introduced in House">Fair Housing for Domestic Violence and Sexual Assault Survivors Act of 2021

 This bill prohibits discrimination against survivors of domestic violence, sexual assault, or sex trafficking in the sale or rental of housing and other related real estate activities.</summary>
